    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class Link
extends org.jgrapht.graph.DefaultWeightedEdge
    This class represents a link in the topology graph. A link has a source and destination node and a subnet address.
    Since:
    October 2, 2013
    Version:
    0.3
